The relationship that parents share with their children is one that impacts a child throughout his or her lifetime. Studies show that the benefits of parental involvement are manifold, affecting numerous areas of a child's life, including "health and development":http://babyutoledo.com/needlink/, "academic progress":http://babyutoledo.com/needlink/, and "life choices":http://babyutoledo.com/needlink/.


